text: They never get my order right.  Usually small things but the last two times have been the worst. Last time, I paid extra for Pan Pizza and I got hand tossed. This time, I ordered Super Supreme and I got Meat Lovers.....

text: I ordered a pizza on the phone to pick up. They said it would be ready in 15 minutes. So I picked it up in 15 minutes as I live just a couple blocks from there. Pizza was cold and there was just a few pieces of spinach and about 8 pieces of …More

name: Linda Zacharias
text: Fresh quality pizza. No dine in. Better to pick up than have delivered.

name: Teresa Brown
text: I haven't eaten at pizza hut for years,  Now I remember why.  The person at the cash reguster made me feel rushed.  I'll admit I didn't know what I wanted.  When I got the $20 pizza it was way under my expiation..  I'll drive down to Costco next time.
